      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STEAL THE STAGE (2) is in sizzling form lately, rocketing around this track in 29.71 to score two back then following on with a 25.10 win over 450m at Shepparton. Smart win two back and looks a key chance here. ABSOLUTE RUPEE (1) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by a neck at Shepparton in a handy 25.32 beating KRIS BAR IMOGEN. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from three attempts. Likely to be in the finish. INDIAN PRINCE (3) is always a threat when he races at this track and distance.",
